### testAPI - Cotizaciones Endpoint Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost/testAPI

### Step 1: Login to get authentication token
POST http://localhost/testAPI/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "emailOrUsername": "alex_smith",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Step 2: Get all cotizaciones (use token from Step 1)
GET http://localhost/testAPI/index.php/api/cotizaciones
X-API-KEY: 782913c20001aa10d22d06bf8425d9ad

###

### Step 3: Get specific cotizacion by ID
GET http://localhost/testAPI/api/cotizaciones?id=1
X-API-KEY: YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Step 4: Create new cotizacion
POST http://localhost/testAPI/api/cotizaciones
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-KEY: YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "code": "SKU_NEW_001",
  "amount": 100,
  "client": "New Client Company",
  "description": "A new quotation for testing purposes"
}

###

### Step 5: Update cotizacion (ID 1)
PUT http://localhost/testAPI/api/cotizaciones
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-KEY: YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "id": 1,
  "code": "SKU_913_UPDATED",
  "amount": 50,
  "client": "Updated Client Name",
  "description": "Updated description for testing"
}

###

### Step 6: Delete cotizacion (ID 51 or any test ID)
DELETE http://localhost/testAPI/api/cotizaciones
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-KEY: YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "id": 51
}

###

### Alternative: Using Bearer Token Format
### Get all cotizaciones with Bearer token
GET http://localhost/testAPI/api/cotizaciones
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###
